# getUUIDValue()

**Instance Method**

If the data element is a UUID (type 3), it returns the value as an IOBluetoothSDPUUID.

## Declaration

```swift
func getUUIDValue() -> IOBluetoothSDPUUID!
```

## Return Value

Returns an IOBluetoothSDPUUID representation of the data element if it is a UUID.
